description:
Create Vue pages in `app/frontend/pages/clients/`:
- **Index.vue**: List view with search input, card/table toggle (persist preference in localStorage). Use existing shadcn Card and Table components
- **Show.vue**: Tabbed interface using shadcn Tabs. Tabs: Overview (contact info, notes), Dogs (list with DogCard), Appointments (recent/upcoming), Invoices (outstanding/history)
- **New.vue / Edit.vue**: Form using shadcn Form components. Fields: name, email, phone, address, notes
- **ClientCard.vue**: Component in `app/frontend/components/` showing avatar, name, dog count, last appointment

Add TypeScript interface to `app/frontend/types/index.d.ts`:
```typescript
interface Client {
  id: number;
  name: string;
  email: string;
  phone?: string;
  address?: string;
  notes?: string;
  dogs_count: number;
  created_at: string;
}
```
